01:23:03,090 --> 01:23:07,181
Well, I could without even
naming the parts you mention.

1133
01:23:07,268 --> 01:23:11,628
A cartesian would look at
the tree and conceptually take...

1134
01:23:11,680 --> 01:23:15,726
