1155
01:24:55,926 --> 01:24:58,180
If one dies, the other dies.

1156
01:24:58,243 --> 01:25:02,565
And there are millions of
relationships like this in our world...

1157
01:25:02,649 --> 01:25:05,409
...each depending on
each other for life.

1158
01:25:07,140 --> 01:25:12,485
The Systems Theory recognizes
this web of relationships...

1159
01:25:12,541 --> 01:25:16,094
...as the essence of all living things.

1160
01:25:16,162 --> 01:25:20,393
