1178
01:26:44,496 --> 01:26:49,626
Yes, it is.
And it means something specific too.

1179
01:26:49,658 --> 01:26:56,937
It means that a living system is
self-maintaining, self-renewing...

1180
01:26:57,001 --> 01:27:00,441
- ...self-transcending.
